ht: 0px; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 20px\">OC GURU ll</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 220px; padding-right: 20px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\"><img title=\"OC GURU ll\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/3/overview/2612.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 650px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 15px\">全新直觉式超频软件，参数调教、监控更方便，可透过OC GURU ll调整核心频率/电压、内存频率/电压、风扇运作模式等，并可直接线胜更新驱动程序、BIOS等</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 12px\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 20px\">单卡最多可支持4台显示器</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 220px; padding-right: 20px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\"><img title=\"Up to 4 displays on a Single Card\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/3/overview/3136.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 650px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 15px\">在开普勒架构中,单一显卡最多可支持到4台显示器.满足你的多屏幕设计,高清晰度和极致的游戏体验</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: b