       <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">6pin/无</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">TDP热功耗设计</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">150瓦</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213,0,0)\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">140瓦</span></span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">65瓦</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">65瓦</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">参考价格</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">2199-2299元</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">1699-1799元</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">799-899元</span></td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">699-799元</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong>●GTX660和GTX660Ti外观对比</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　GTX660Ti，NV的战略是主要发展AIC非公版，因为市面上的公版产品相当少有。而这次发布的GTX660和GTX650，产品数量都相当多，覆盖公版非公版。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>&nbsp;</span><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"外观对比\" alt=\"外观对比\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_GTX660VS660ti_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX660\" alt=\"GTX660\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_IMG_1399_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX660\" alt=\"GTX660\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_IMG_1404_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\nGTX660和GTX660Ti区别在哪里？</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　GTX660和GTX660Ti外观上基本一样，穿着一样的外壳，一样散热器，一样的PCB，而且最大区别在于，GTX660只有一个6pin供电接口和SLI接口，而且GTX660Ti则各有两个。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"显卡外观对比\" alt=\"显卡外观对比\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_pcb_PK6670_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\nPCB规模对比</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　正如一样的PCB板子，也是跟市面上499元价格的入门显卡一样大小。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong>●GTX650和GT640外观对比</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　我们从映众得到一块以公版PCB（散热器非公版）设计的GTX650和GT640，可以看到两款显卡的体积基本一样，就散热器的区别。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX650\" alt=\"GTX650\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_yingzhong_4_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX650\" alt=\"GTX650\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_IMG_1433_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX650\" alt=\"GTX650\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_IMG_1434_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\nGTX650和GT640显卡区别在哪里？</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　要分辨GTX650和GT640却有点困难。GTX650一般都带有一个6pin供电接口，普通的GT640则不需要供电，但一些高频版的GT640依然设计有单6pin供电。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img title=\"GTX650\" alt=\"GTX650\" src=\"http://img0.pconline.com.cn/pconline/1209/13/2940961_yingzhong_3_thumb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; width: 500px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\nPCB规模对比</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　GTX650定位入门级，我们都看到PCB板跟市售399元的GT430有一拼，说不定日后会见到GTX650做成的高清卡。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">　　GTX660的外观并没有让我们感到特别，而且GTX650的超小规模PCB板都可谓震惊，毕竟这是带有&ldquo;GTX&rdquo;字眼的显卡，性能也不会差到哪里去。实际真的如此？下面我们将为大家揭晓</p>\r\n</span></p>','images/201311/thumb_img/5670_thumb_G_1383705676200.jpg','images/201311/goods_img/5670_G_1383705676353.jpg','images/201311/source_img/5670_G_1383705676224.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1383705676','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1396037127','5','','2','0','0','0');
