olor: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">价格</a>有所顾忌的话，GeForce GTX 760的价格则实属厚道。而我们今天为读者带来的，就是一款采用非公版设计的<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>&mdash;&mdash;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">耕昇</a><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">GTX760</a>关羽版。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"标配三风扇 耕昇GTX760关羽版性能测试\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/115_500x2000/79/ce150Km6m64.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n耕昇GTX760关羽版</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 耕昇GTX760关羽版采用基于28nm制程工艺，Kepler架构设计的GK104图形核心。该<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">显卡</a>拥有1152个流<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">处理器</a>、32个ROPs单元和96个纹理单元。完美支持DirectX 11游戏特效、CUDA、PhysX物理加速、SLI双卡互联等技术。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"标配三风扇 耕昇GTX760关羽版性能测试\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/115_500x2000/277/cedBLijqrK5eE.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n显卡PCB设计</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 耕昇GTX760关羽版采用非公版PCB设计，供电部分采用核心与显存独立的供电方案，元器件采用全固态电容与全封闭电感，辅以8+8pin外接供电接口，为显卡的稳定运行及超频提供了充足的保障。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"标配三风扇 耕昇GTX760关羽版性能测试\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/115_500x2000/323/cego2yILhjWvo.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n显卡供电方案</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 耕昇GTX760关羽版搭载<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">GDDR5</a>高速显存颗粒，显存容量2048MB，显存位宽<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">256Bit</a>，显卡的默认频率为1110/6008MHz。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"标配三风扇 耕昇GTX760关羽版性能测试\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/115_500x2000/266/ceer5mAfLCHI.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n显卡散热系统</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 耕昇GTX760关羽版搭载全覆盖、开放式<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">散热器</a>，铜质散热底座能够将核心温度快速传导至鳍片，再由风扇快速排出，在保证散热的同时还提供了不错的噪音控制。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"outline-style: none; color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"标配三风扇 耕昇GTX760关羽版性能测试\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/115_500x2000/295/ceyPKE6XwSHxQ.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></a><br />\r\n视频输出接口</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 耕昇GTX760关羽版采用DVI+HDMI+双Mini DisplayPort输出组合，支持市面上绝大多数<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">显示器</a>的接口需要。同时该显卡支持单卡多屏技术，满足了不同用户对显卡的不同使用需要。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: simsun; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● 测试平台硬件环境一览</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为保证测试能够发挥<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">显卡</a>的最佳性能，本次测试平台由<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">Intel酷睿i7</a>-3970X<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">处理器</a>、<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">技嘉</a>X79芯片组<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">主板</a>、威刚<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">4GB</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; outline-style: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">DDR3</a>-1600&times;4四通道<a s