</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/0D/rBEQWVEmDa4IAAAAAACuUp-8ngkAAA3UgMQQjQAAK5q406.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/0D/rBEQWFEmDaYIAAAAAAB9vkC1xksAAA3UgNs1T4AAH3W587.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">产品功能Product Function</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">SD卡性能等级介绍</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">按照 SDA协会阐述的，Class是用来描述最低连续传输速度的标记。连续传输速度在4MB/s以上的称谓CLASS 4, CLASS 6则是连续传输速度在6MB/s以上，目前最高的是CLASS10。需要提醒的是，各个存储卡生产厂商在使用CLASS等级标记时也有自己的速度规范标准。CLASS等级主要参考价值在连续摄像情况，CLASS4可以使用高清1080P状况下的录像。SanDisk SD卡，理论读写速度达到15MB/s,但仍然使用CLASS 4的标记。而部分厂商，则为商业目的，标高CLASS等级，来蒙蔽不知情的消费者，结果在录像视出现图像断续的现象。所以在选购SD系列产品时，要注意产品的实际读写速度，而并不要只看CALSS等级。该 SD/SDHC 可兼容读卡器将帮助并确保您将 SD 格式转换为 SDHC 格式&ndash;适用于我们的卡和可兼容的主机设备。 存储卡基于 SD 2.0 规格在速度和性能方面的等级被分为 4 类。SDHC 存储卡是高度安全、邮票大小的闪存卡，可用于以下各种数码产品：数码音乐播放器、掌上个人电脑 (HPC)、数码相机、数码视频摄像机、智能电话、汽车定位系统和电子书籍，并且符合 SD 2.00 规格。 SDHC 卡具有用于保护有版权数据的安全特性。</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">SD卡存储容量介绍</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/0D/rBEQWVEmDjkIAAAAAAJCxIjHjzAAAA3VAAwAkcAAkLc980.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/0D/rBEQWFEmDkoIAAAAAAMVX_nA--UAAA3VAEEOMsAAxV3881.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">售后服务After-Sales Service</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/0D/rBEQWFEmDm0IAAAAAAJGG5SriNEAAA3VAIUDxUAAkYz430.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 25px; font-size: 12px\">此产品提供五年保固和免费技术支持服务，专业售后团队为您服务，保障您的权益。</span></div>\r\n</div>','images/201311/thumb_img/5824_thumb_G_1383884370464.jpg','images/201311/goods_img/5824_G_1383884370315.jpg','images/201311/source_img/5824_G_1383884370126.png','1','','1','1','0','0','1383881205','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1398296256','65','','0','0','0','0');
