//www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 20px\">DVI Support</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 160px\"><img title=\"DVI Support\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/1823.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 710px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify\">DVI 影像传输介面可传送未经压缩的影像资料, 并且最佳化数位显示设备的画面品质, 例如 LCD 萤幕, 数位投影机等. 此外, DVI介面也和HDCP(High-bandwidth Digital Content Protection)相容.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 20px\">全新的技嘉App Center（应用软件管理中心）</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 160px\"><img title=\"全新的技嘉App Center（应用软件管理中心）\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/3207.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 710px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0px; display: table; border-collapse: separate; border-right-color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-color: rgb(0,0,0); -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-color: rgb